title: Walnut & Padauk Decorative Segmented Bowl
description: A wood combination hard to beat...Walnut and Padauk. This bowl is 9" in diameter and 6" in height, and is composed of 112 segments. "Vivid" is a good word to describe the Padauk rim on this beauty. Use your imagination and come up with your wood types and I'll custom make one of these for you!
